Included is the tarball of www/suphp06, which is the port of suPHP 0.6.2
(http://www.suphp.org/).

Fix: * Repo-copy ports/www/suphp to ports/www/suphp06;

* cvs rm ports/www/suphp06/files/patch-*;

* Untar the attached tarball under ports/;

* Add to www/suphp/Makefile: CONFLICTS=	suphp-0.6.*
How-To-Repeat: N/A
